    g(x) &= -2nx^2 -2nx + \dfrac{2n^2}{-2n} \\[8pt]
    &= -2nx^2 - 2nx - n
    \end{align*}
    $$

    And given that $g(1)=3$,

    $$
    \begin{align*}
    g(1) &= -2n(1)^2 - 2n(1) - n \\[8pt]
